title: Does Bobby Make It Onto The Jury? + Will It Uber: Proposal Edition

description:
Bobby highlights his jury duty experience. Lunchbox attempts to Uber an engagement ring AND tries to get the driver to propose to Morgan #2. Also, the show shares their trivial "Cry Me A River" life situations.
